{{Politics of Bolivia}}
A province is the second largest administrative division in [[Bolivia]], after a [[Departments of Bolivia|department]]. Each department is divided into [[province]]s. There are 112 [[province]]s.
The country's provinces are further divided into 337 [[Municipalities of Bolivia|municipalities]] which are administered by an [[alcalde]] and [[municipal council]].
